Daily Maverick in partnership with eNCA is hosting a series of panel discussions at the Cape Town International Convention, on Friday.  SPONSORED - Daily Maverick in partnership with eNCA is hosting a series of panel discussions at the Cape Town International Convention on Friday. Stats SA has revealed that the country has entered into a recession. State-owned entities are in shambles and unemployment continue to rise. It’s time to change the narrative. It’s 2020. South Africa needs 20/20 vision more than ever. It’s time for hope. It’s time for action. It’s time to help Rebuild South Africa. The Gathering wants to inspire South Africans to take action in rebuilding the country.